description: Boost your cloud skills. You will be catching up in no time! This tutorial gives an overview of the AWS cloud. It will teach you AWS concepts, services, security, architecture, and pricing. In addition, this tutorial will help you prepare for the AWS Certified Cloud Practitioner Exam. This skill offers many job opportunities. AWS is one of the major cloud providers. You can do everything in the AWS cloud. Format: Text and video. Prerequisites: None. Time to complete: Eight hours. Content collaboration: W3schools.com collaborates with Amazon Web Services on this tutorial to deliver digital training content to our students.
